WEBVTT

00:00.888 --> 00:03.254
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>The Borgias...</i>

00:03.321 --> 00:06.758
Habemus papam!

00:06.826 --> 00:09.324
You are aware, Holy Father,
of the plots against you?

00:09.392 --> 00:12.091
Oh, what would Rome
be without a good plot?

00:12.192 --> 00:13.489
Simony!

00:13.556 --> 00:14.923
I have evidence that
will bring this house

00:14.991 --> 00:16.722
crashing down
around your ears.

00:16.823 --> 00:17.788
Evidence?

00:17.856 --> 00:19.256
Of lechery!

00:19.324 --> 00:22.663
All of Rome knows you're
the mother to my children.

00:22.731 --> 00:24.900
The pope must be
seen to be chaste.

00:24.968 --> 00:26.738
God has chosen us

00:26.806 --> 00:29.641
to sweep the Vatican
clean of corruption.

00:29.709 --> 00:32.343
What Rome needs now is-

00:32.411 --> 00:33.976
You.

00:34.043 --> 00:36.444
Don't you want them to hear
that you have a new whore?

00:36.513 --> 00:39.415
Whom can one trust,
in this Rome of ours?

00:39.483 --> 00:41.650
I believe trust needs
to be earned, my lord.

00:41.717 --> 00:43.217
Somebody!

00:43.319 --> 00:44.585
Perhaps it has been.

00:44.653 --> 00:46.922
The vultures are
circling our family.

00:47.023 --> 00:48.558
Our Rome.

00:50.728 --> 00:53.197
It seems Cardinal
Della Rovere has fled.

00:53.265 --> 00:54.498
Your Royal Highness.

00:54.599 --> 00:55.899
What do you want?

00:55.967 --> 00:58.567
I want Naples to join
in alliance with me

00:58.669 --> 00:59.936
to rid the papacy-

01:00.037 --> 01:01.204
Of the stench of Borgia.

01:01.272 --> 01:03.072
Give me control
of the papal armies

01:03.139 --> 01:04.239
and I will
protect us all.

01:04.307 --> 01:06.841
We will have one
son in the cloth-

01:06.942 --> 01:08.609
-and one in armour.

01:08.677 --> 01:09.943
You think it fits me,
Brother?

01:10.044 --> 01:11.544
And Lucrezia must marry!

01:11.612 --> 01:12.912
Bind our enemies to us!

01:12.980 --> 01:14.313
Make friends of them.

01:14.381 --> 01:16.648
And if my husband
proves ungallant?

01:18.117 --> 01:20.285
I shall cut his heart
out with a dinner knife.

01:21.654 --> 01:23.021
Lucrezia!

01:23.089 --> 01:25.224
Have you any friends
you can confide in?

01:25.325 --> 01:26.926
There is a groom.
Paolo.

01:27.027 --> 01:28.094
My lady.

01:28.161 --> 01:29.462
Young lovers are
always doomed.

01:31.032 --> 01:32.032
Lucrezia!

01:32.133 --> 01:33.200
I am with child.

01:33.268 --> 01:35.369
Thank God, not my husband's.

01:35.437 --> 01:38.171
Your Royal Highness,
King Charles of France.

01:38.239 --> 01:40.641
I want to restore the
Universal Church.

01:40.708 --> 01:42.142
To her former dignity.

01:42.210 --> 01:44.177
You will have
your war!

01:44.245 --> 01:48.047
But it will be fought
the French way.

01:48.115 --> 01:50.115
Holy Father,
we should abandon Rome.

01:50.217 --> 01:53.485
We will not tolerate
this heresy!

01:53.552 --> 01:55.219
The barbarians
are approaching!

01:55.287 --> 01:56.520
We shall outwit them.

01:56.588 --> 01:58.222
I know little of
the art of war.

01:58.289 --> 02:00.057
Thank God someone
in this family does.

02:00.125 --> 02:02.828
You are either with us-

02:02.895 --> 02:04.129
Or against us.

02:04.230 --> 02:06.298
Fire!

02:08.634 --> 02:10.669
We could be said to
have an understanding.

02:10.770 --> 02:12.238
We could indeed.

02:12.339 --> 02:15.475
The crown of Naples.

02:15.542 --> 02:18.377
King Charles will not
remain in Naples for long.

02:18.445 --> 02:19.945
Plague.

02:20.013 --> 02:21.814
Did the Borgia
Pope know of this?

02:21.881 --> 02:24.216
We should thank God
for all the blessings

02:24.283 --> 02:29.420
he has visited
upon this, our family.

